categories: Category:Rulers of the Empress Teta system

nodes.text: Alor Keto was a male member of the Keto family who ruled as the Emperor of the planet Empress Teta during the Imperial Era. Keto's rule lasted several decades, but was weak and ineffectual, and Keto himself was a puppet of the Mining Guild. During Keto's rule, his health began to decline. His niece, Eara Lota, was the rightful heir of Empress Teta.
